{"lemma":"جَرَسِ","slug":"جَرَسِ","root":"ج.ر.س","root_slug":"ج-ر-س","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ر-س","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n5526","n5529","n5530","n5531"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to ring, to produce a gentle modulating sound"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to suck, to eat with the tongue (said of certain animals)","tags":["archaic"],"examples":[{"text":"لَاعِيَة شجرة تنبت في سفح الجبال لها ورق طيّب الرِيح تجرسه النَحْل وله لبن غزير إذا قطِعَت","english":"Green spurge or sun spurge is a shrub which grows on the surfaces of mountains, it has good-smelling leaves sucked by bees and copious milk when slit."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gong, bell, tam-tam"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n5526","headword_ar":"جَرَسَ","root":"jrs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [aor., app.,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", as seems to be implied in the K, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarosN","text_ar":"جَرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which see below,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, made a sound;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajrs","text_ar":"اجرس","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh, TA:) [or both signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, made a low, gentle, slight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft, sound;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as appears from what follows.] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarasa biAlkalaAmi","text_ar":"جَرَسَ بِالكَلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarasa AlkalaAma","text_ar":"جَرَسَ الكَلَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spoke in a low, gentle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft, voice"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tone;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with modulation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"melody;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nagama fiyhi","text_ar":"نَغَمَ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nagama bihi","text_ar":"نَغَمَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarasa","text_ar":"جَرَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarosN","text_ar":"جَرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tjr~K","text_ar":"تجرٍّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spoke:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he said a thing, and spoke in a low, gentle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft, voice"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with modulation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"melody;"},{"kind":"text","text":"expl. by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"takal~ama","text_ar":"تَكَلَّمَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi$aYo'K watanag~ama","text_ar":"بِشَىْءٍ وَتَنَغَّمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lth, S.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajrs","text_ar":"اجرس","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also used in the senses here following."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a bird)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused the sound of its passing to be heard:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, * K:) and in like manner it is said of a man. (K, accord. to the TA; but not found by me in any copy of the K.) ↓ And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an ornament,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloYN","text_ar":"حَلْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made a sound"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, * K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like that of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaras","text_ar":"جَرَس"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bell"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Anjrs","text_ar":"انجرس","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, TA.) ↓ And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a tribe,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaY~N","text_ar":"حَىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made its sound"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaros","text_ar":"جَرْس"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be heard:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to the T,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made the sound of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaros","text_ar":"جَرْس"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a thing to be heard."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ↓ And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raised his voice."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ↓ And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel-driver)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sang"},{"kind":"text","text":"to camels"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the purpose of urging"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exciting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raised his voice in doing so."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b2-  [Hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarasa","text_ar":"جَرَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, AO, S, K,) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarosN","text_ar":"جَرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, AO, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ate"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a thing: because a slight sound is made in doing so]: (AO, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he licked"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a thing]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his tongue."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarasat Aln~aHolu AlEurofuTa","text_ar":"جَرَسَت النَّحْلُ العُرْفُطَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The bees ate the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trees called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ErfT","text_ar":"عرفط"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarasati Aln~awora","text_ar":"جَرَسَتِ النَّوْرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, A,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEasala","text_ar":"العَسَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[put tropically for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~awora","text_ar":"النَّوْرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"because honey is made from flowers or blossoms], (Lth, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the bees ate the flowers, or blossoms, making a sound in so doing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"licked the flowers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blossoms, and thence made honey."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarasati","text_ar":"جَرَسَتِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaA$iyapu Al$~ajara","text_ar":"المَاشِيَةُ الشَّجَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEu$oba","text_ar":"العُشْبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beasts licked the trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the herbage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarasati Albaqarapu","text_ar":"جَرَسَتِ البَقَرَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waladahaA","text_ar":"وَلَدَهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The cow licked her young one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","TA","A","Msb","S","K","Lth","AO"]},{"entry_id":"n5529","headword_ar":"جَرْسٌ","root":"jrs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jirosN","text_ar":"جِرْسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarasN","text_ar":"جَرَسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, ISd)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sound:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, A, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a low, faint, gentle, slight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft, sound:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, S A, K:) such, for instance, as the sound of the beaks of birds, (S, A, Msb,) pecking, (A,) upon a thing which they are eating: (S:) and that of bees eating flowers or blossoms: (A:) and of a tribe [or crowd of men, more particularly as heard from some distance; i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hum"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) and of a camel-driver singing to his beasts to urge or excite them: (A:) and the slight sound of a letter of the alphabet: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"low, gentle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft, speech:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or when the word is used alone, [i. e., not coupled with another noun as it is in the second of the two examples here following,] it is with fet-h: thus one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA samiEotu lahu jarosFA","text_ar":"مَا سَمِعْتُ لَهُ جَرْسًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, K;) i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I heard not any sound of him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) but you say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA samiEotu lahu His~FA walaA jirosFA","text_ar":"مَا سَمِعْتُ لَهُ حِسًّا وَلَا جِرْسًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr; (A, K;) i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I heard not any motion, nor any sound, of him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hs","text_ar":"حس"},{"kind":"text","text":":) pl. [app. of the third]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajoraAsN","text_ar":"اَجْرَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ham p. 200.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaro$N","text_ar":"جَرْشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb","K","Kr","ISd","ISk","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n5530","headword_ar":"جِرْسٌ","root":"jrs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next precedes, in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n5531","headword_ar":"جَرَسٌ","root":"jrs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bell;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing well known;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing that is hung to the neck of the camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c., and that makes a sound:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or, accord. to some, the ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little round bell called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"julojul","text_ar":"جُلْجُل"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which is struck"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to make it sound"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Lth, S, K:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing that is struck by the Christians at the times of prayers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 616:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^joraAsN","text_ar":"اجْرَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh, Msb.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taSoHabu AlmalaAy^ikapu","text_ar":"لَا تَصْحَبُ المَلَايِكَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rufoqapF fiyhaA jarasN","text_ar":"رُفْقَةً فِيهَا جَرَسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The angels will not accompany an assemblage of persons journeying together among whom is a bell"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, TA:) the reason is said to be, because it guides others to them; for Mo- hammad liked not to let the enemy know of his approach until he came upon them suddenly. (TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarosN","text_ar":"جَرْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K","TA","Lth"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}